To: The United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs (UN DESA)
Subject: Expression of Interest for Special Accreditation - UN 2026 Water Conference

On behalf of GNAIAAAC LLC, I am writing to formally request special accreditation for the UN 2026 Water Conference in Abu Dhabi.

GNAIAAAC LLC is a technology-focused infrastructure entity dedicated to resolving global water bankruptcy through the "Vital Science Grid." Our work aligns directly with SDG 6 (Clean Water and Sanitation) by integrating AI-native monitoring with decentralized energy systems to power water purification and distribution in underserved regions, including the USA, Bangladesh, and India.

We intend to contribute to the "Water for Prosperity" and "Water for Planet" interactive dialogues by sharing our technical framework for 100% Carbon Fiber infrastructure and resonant energy grids.

Signed,

Arifur Shanta
CEO & Lead Architect, GNAIAAAC LLC
